CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 13, 1956, pg. A15, reads: "Carver Committee Meets - The first meeting of the "George Washington Carver Week" committee was held in lounge of the Council of Churches, Seated are Dr. Elizabeth Graf, Robert V. Cresswell and Mrs. Alma Illery. Standing, Mrs. Lillian Friedberg, Dr. J. Allan Figurel and Mrs. M.D. Chamberlain. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of George Washington Carver Week committee, seated from left: Dr. Elizabeth Graf, Robert V. Cresswell, Alma Illery; standing: Lillian Friedberg, Dr. J. Allan Figurel, and Mrs. M. D. Chamberlain, gathered at table in lounge of Council of Churches
